<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:04:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国外交部称中印将加快边界谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-india-speed-up-border-talks-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国外交部周四在一份声明中表示，中印将加快围绕有争议边界的谈判，继续维护该地区的和平与安宁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 00:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-india-speed-up-border-talks-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：前外交官表示，如果特朗普获胜，朝鲜希望重启核谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-wants-restart-nuclear-talks-if-trump-wins-says-ex-diplomat-2024-07-31/</link><description>一位最近叛逃到韩国的朝鲜高级外交官告诉路透社，如果唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统，朝鲜希望与美国重新开启核谈判，并正在努力制定新的谈判策略。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:09:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-wants-restart-nuclear-talks-if-trump-wins-says-ex-diplomat-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰泽连斯基希望中国对俄罗斯施加更大压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-does-not-want-china-mediator-2024-07-31/</link><description>乌克兰总统泽连斯基周三表示，基辅不希望中国在与俄罗斯长达29个月的冲突中充当调解人，但希望北京向莫斯科施加更大压力，以结束战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-does-not-want-china-mediator-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：非凡的反弹席卷了所有市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-31/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 21:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>游泳——中国选手潘金莲打破自己保持的1亿米自由泳金牌世界纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-chinas-pan-obliterates-100m-freestyle-world-record-gold-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，中国选手潘占乐在巴黎奥运会上打破了自己保持的100米自由泳世界纪录，在该项目中夺得了令人震惊的金牌，并击败了众多冠军对手。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-chinas-pan-obliterates-100m-freestyle-world-record-gold-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>由于翻新商品需求稳定，eBay 季度业绩超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ebay-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-07-31/</link><description>受对二手商品、具有成本效益的汽车零部件和配件的强劲需求的推动，eBay 对第二季度收入和利润的预期超出了华尔街的预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ebay-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者寻求阻止中国企业获得太阳能制造补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-lawmakers-seek-block-chinese-firms-solar-manufacturing-subsidy-2024-07-31/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周三提出了一项法案，禁止中国太阳能电池板制造商为其美国工厂申请补贴。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-lawmakers-seek-block-chinese-firms-solar-manufacturing-subsidy-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国反兴奋剂机构指责《纽约时报》蓄意破坏报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-anti-doping-agency-accuses-new-york-times-sabotage-over-latest-report-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国反兴奋剂机构（CHINADA）指责《纽约时报》将兴奋剂问题政治化，并表示该刊物试图“影响巴黎奥运会上中国运动员的心理”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-anti-doping-agency-accuses-new-york-times-sabotage-over-latest-report-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻称，美国考虑对中国获取人工智能存储芯片实施新限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-mulls-new-curbs-chinas-access-ai-memory-chips-bloomberg-news-says-2024-07-31/</link><description>据彭博社周三报道，美国正在考虑单方面限制中国获取人工智能存储芯片，例如美光科技和 SK 海力士制造的芯片以及能够制造此类半导体的设备，最快将于下个月进行。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-mulls-new-curbs-chinas-access-ai-memory-chips-bloomberg-news-says-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>国防部长称加拿大军舰通过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canadian-warship-transited-through-taiwan-strait-defense-minister-says-2024-07-31/</link><description>加拿大国防部长表示，一艘加拿大军舰最近通过台湾海峡，重申了加拿大对“自由、开放和包容”的印太地区的承诺。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canadian-warship-transited-through-taiwan-strait-defense-minister-says-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与美国海军在南海举行联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-navy-hold-joint-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-07-31/</link><description>菲律宾武装部队表示，菲律宾和美国海军周三在南海举行了联合海上演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-navy-hold-joint-exercise-south-china-sea-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>BMX-阿根廷和中国队在自由泳比赛中夺得金牌，但热门球队却惨遭淘汰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/bmx-chinas-deng-takes-gold-womens-freestyle-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，在巴黎炎热的阳光下，首次参加奥运会的阿根廷和中国选手在 BMX 自由式决赛中夺得金牌，一连串戏剧性的撞车事故将卫冕奖牌得主击倒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:14:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/bmx-chinas-deng-takes-gold-womens-freestyle-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国预计未来五年城镇化率接近70%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国务院周三表示，预计未来五年常住人口城镇化率将提高到接近70%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-expects-urbanisation-rate-near-70-next-five-years-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球——中国新科王王惨遭淘汰；年轻的勒布伦占上风</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-newly-crowned-wang-suffers-shock-elimination-by-swedish-2024-07-31/</link><description>庆祝乒乓球混双金牌后不到24小时，中国选手王楚钦周三在单打比赛中惨遭瑞典选手特鲁斯·莫加德淘汰，后者随后进入四分之一决赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-newly-crowned-wang-suffers-shock-elimination-by-swedish-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>优步与比亚迪合作将电动汽车引入全球网约车平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/uber-byd-partner-bring-evs-ride-hailing-platform-globally-2024-07-31/</link><description>过去两年，电动汽车的高价格和借贷成本的增加成为了电动汽车采用的障碍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/uber-byd-partner-bring-evs-ride-hailing-platform-globally-2024-07-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>